WEBVTT

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:24.879
Kid

00:01:27.959 --> 00:01:28.879
You're Chen Fan, right?

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:30.159
Someone paid us

00:01:30.159 --> 00:01:31.280
to break your hand

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.560
Do you know what day it is?

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:34.599
Police are patrolling everywhere outside

00:01:34.599 --> 00:01:35.400
None of you will get away

00:01:35.599 --> 00:01:36.920
Your daddy doesn't scare easily

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:37.640
Be a good boy

00:01:38.079 --> 00:01:39.159
and let us break your hand

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.079
Or else you're not leaving today

00:01:45.959 --> 00:01:46.560
Do it

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:55.439
I dare you to come over

00:01:58.159 --> 00:01:58.519
Speak

00:01:58.640 --> 00:01:59.439
Who sent you?

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:02.159
Talk!

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:05.480
Huang Hu

00:02:14.759 --> 00:02:15.560
Bro, get in the car, quick

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:17.599
Go

00:02:17.960 --> 00:02:18.479
Boss

00:02:19.360 --> 00:02:20.000
Run

00:02:22.680 --> 00:02:23.400
Why are you here?

00:02:24.039 --> 00:02:25.520
I saw you run out suddenly

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.000
I was worried, so I came over

00:02:28.800 --> 00:02:29.039
Bro

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:30.000
don't panic

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:31.080
I'm taking you to the hospital now

00:02:31.199 --> 00:02:31.719
Go back for the exam

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:33.240
There's an infirmary at the exam site entrance

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:34.000
But Bro

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:35.719
how can you take the exam like this?

00:02:35.759 --> 00:02:36.960
Three years of work for this one shot

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.280
No matter the result

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.439
I won't allow you to be absent

00:02:39.879 --> 00:02:41.159
I still want to be schoolmates with Ruochu

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:44.840
Chen Fan

00:02:45.039 --> 00:02:46.080
Once you miss the Gaokao

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:47.560
let's see what you have left to fight me with

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.240
Doctor, please hurry

00:02:50.360 --> 00:02:51.560
We still have to take the Gaokao

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.439
Bro, bear with it

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:54.199
It'll be over soon

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:05.479
Report

00:03:06.159 --> 00:03:07.599
Student, why are you so late?

00:03:08.120 --> 00:03:08.759
I injured my hand

00:03:08.759 --> 00:03:09.520
and went to get it bandaged

00:03:10.360 --> 00:03:11.319
Let me see your Exam Admission Ticket

00:03:14.280 --> 00:03:14.680
Take a seat

00:03:15.039 --> 00:03:15.599
Thank you, teacher

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:18.000
That idiot Red Hair

00:03:18.199 --> 00:03:18.960
Good for nothing but screwing up

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:20.840
Wasting your daddy's money

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.319
Hey

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:31.960
Chen Fan

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:33.039
What do you want?

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:37.479
Your friend's

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:39.120
Don't pull these stunts anymore

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:40.560
Good luck with the exam

00:03:49.039 --> 00:03:50.360
To make money these days

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:53.400
it's just buying real estate, mines, or stocks

00:03:54.479 --> 00:03:56.199
If I had the startup capital

00:03:56.479 --> 00:03:57.759
I'd buy an apartment in Puxi first

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:59.879
then buy up Moutai stock like crazy

00:04:01.240 --> 00:04:02.479
But where will the money come from?

00:04:11.319 --> 00:04:11.639
Oh man

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:12.879
One step too late

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.759
Otherwise I'd be Pony Chen

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:19.439
But this internet wave is just starting

00:04:20.199 --> 00:04:21.560
I can succeed at whatever I do

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:23.920
Bro, here

00:04:25.319 --> 00:04:25.600
No thanks

00:04:25.879 --> 00:04:26.680
I drink sugar-free

00:04:27.480 --> 00:04:28.720
Since when is there sugar-free cola?

00:04:30.319 --> 00:04:30.839
Hey, Bro

00:04:31.399 --> 00:04:33.079
That thing you told me yesterday...

00:04:33.079 --> 00:04:34.360
It's a secret

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:34.839
What is it?

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:36.319
Just this

00:04:36.759 --> 00:04:37.560
Do you have a QQ number?

00:04:38.399 --> 00:04:39.480
We registered them together

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:40.120
Don't you remember?

00:04:40.759 --> 00:04:41.319
Let me tell you

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:42.680
You should take this chance now

00:04:42.680 --> 00:04:44.959
Hoard a few 5 or 6-digit QQ numbers

00:04:45.240 --> 00:04:46.079
Sell them in a few years

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:47.160
And you'll make money

00:04:48.279 --> 00:04:48.800
No, wait

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.720
These are free to register

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.800
Who would pay for them?

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:53.519
These QQ numbers...

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:54.279
in the future...

00:04:54.759 --> 00:04:56.160
the shorter, the more valuable.

00:04:56.560 --> 00:04:57.480
So according to your logic,

00:04:57.560 --> 00:04:58.879
the shorter the number string, the more it's worth.

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:00.360
Then would a string of letters...

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.319
be worth even more money?

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:03.199
You're thinking on the right track

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.199
That can really make money

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:07.160
Huh?

00:05:07.319 --> 00:05:08.800
Letters starting with three Ws

00:05:08.800 --> 00:05:10.560
What, what W?

00:05:11.600 --> 00:05:13.720
As long as I can grab those good domain names first

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:15.839
Or build a real domain registration

00:05:15.839 --> 00:05:16.839
and trading platform

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:18.680
By then,

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.959
Ruochu will be able to live a good life with me

00:05:22.759 --> 00:05:23.199
Guo Shuai

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:24.800
The future tech titan

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.319
is about to be born

00:05:26.519 --> 00:05:27.240
Titan?

00:05:28.240 --> 00:05:29.720
You mean tangerine?

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:30.439
Come on, let's go to the internet cafe

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:31.199
Now?

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:31.800
Yeah, don't sit down

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:32.600
Let's go, let's go to the internet cafe

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:33.160
Go to the internet cafe?

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:33.759
Chen Fan

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.240
You can't sit still right after exams?

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:39.439
What did you say before?

00:05:39.519 --> 00:05:40.600
Going to the internet cafe again?

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:41.959
I have serious business at the internet cafe

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:43.720
What serious business can you have there?

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:45.759
I need to learn some computer skills in advance

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.000
Otherwise, when I get to college,

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.120
compared to those who started young,

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:49.279
the gap will be too big

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:51.000
Really?

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:51.199
Yeah

00:05:53.639 --> 00:05:55.680
You can't learn computers at an internet cafe

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:57.199
Let's go

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:59.680
I'll take you to my neighbor, Brother Honghai

00:06:00.839 --> 00:06:01.439
I'm sorry

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.920
I can't fix this computer here

00:06:03.519 --> 00:06:04.240
Then is there anywhere nearby...

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:06.199
where I can get this computer fixed?

00:06:06.759 --> 00:06:07.639
Nearby...

00:06:07.639 --> 00:06:08.240
Brother Honghai

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:09.040
Hey

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:09.600
Ruochu

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:10.160
What brings you here?

00:06:10.879 --> 00:06:12.240
This is my classmate, Chen Fan

00:06:12.680 --> 00:06:13.759
He wants to learn about computers here

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:14.639
Oh

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:18.519
An IBM A-series high-end computer

00:06:19.920 --> 00:06:20.680
Hey, what's wrong with it?

00:06:21.279 --> 00:06:22.480
Hey, wait, don't touch it

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:23.759
You can't afford to pay if you break it

00:06:24.519 --> 00:06:25.120
It's okay

00:06:25.279 --> 00:06:26.040
Let him try

00:06:26.279 --> 00:06:27.879
Just treat it as a last resort

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:30.839
Then I'll give it a try

00:06:33.920 --> 00:06:34.759
This is the latest model

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:35.879
The warranty shouldn't have expired

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:36.920
So I won't open it up

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:39.399
Did you recently get someone

00:06:39.399 --> 00:06:40.879
to install programs or software?

00:06:41.800 --> 00:06:44.000
I did ask someone to install some things last week

00:06:44.519 --> 00:06:45.759
Could that be the reason?

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:47.879
The system configuration file is corrupted

00:06:47.879 --> 00:06:48.600
I'll adjust it for you

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:01.720
It's fixed

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:02.720
It's really fixed

00:07:02.959 --> 00:07:03.839
Thank you

00:07:08.040 --> 00:07:09.800
This kid knows his stuff

00:07:09.879 --> 00:07:11.839
Here, you solved a big problem for me

00:07:11.959 --> 00:07:12.800
You deserve this

00:07:12.839 --> 00:07:13.279
Oh, no, no, no

00:07:13.759 --> 00:07:15.000
Boss Zhou here is the owner

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:15.879
You should give it to him

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:18.040
Oh, no, no, well...

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:19.279
Just take it

00:07:19.319 --> 00:07:19.759
Thanks

00:07:20.079 --> 00:07:20.759
I'm heading out now

00:07:20.959 --> 00:07:21.399
Ruochu

00:07:21.600 --> 00:07:22.639
I don't think this classmate of yours

00:07:22.639 --> 00:07:23.879
needs to learn computers here

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:28.120
Oh, Brother Honghai

00:07:28.759 --> 00:07:30.040
Actually, I have a favor to ask

00:07:30.839 --> 00:07:31.959
I'd like to borrow a computer for a few days

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:33.079
To set up a few domains

00:07:33.439 --> 00:07:34.000
And build a website

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:35.439
Domains?

00:07:36.439 --> 00:07:36.959
A website?

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:41.519
In the year 2000, the domestic internet was just taking off

00:07:42.160 --> 00:07:43.680
All kinds of websites were just popping up

00:07:45.639 --> 00:07:47.560
Ruochu introduced me to Zhou Honghai

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:48.759
They were neighbors

00:07:49.879 --> 00:07:51.600
I successfully built a website platform

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:53.959
Dedicated to domain registration and trading services

00:07:54.759 --> 00:07:56.920
In my past life, a platform just like this

00:07:57.279 --> 00:07:58.839
caught HiChina's eye in the year 2000

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:00.439
The acquisition price was as high as one million

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:03.079
That was one million back in the millennium

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:04.720
This time,

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:07.079
I must get this platform up and running first

00:08:07.439 --> 00:08:08.519
Build up the traffic and resources

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:12.040
And make it a target HiChina can't ignore

00:08:17.519 --> 00:08:18.000
Done

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:18.839
It's ready

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:20.480
What's ready?

00:08:24.079 --> 00:08:25.079
DomainNet

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:27.360
It's actually just a website

00:08:27.759 --> 00:08:28.600
used for trading domains

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:29.800
Oh

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:31.360
Your website looks pretty comprehensive

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:32.720
When do you plan to launch?

00:08:34.120 --> 00:08:34.919
Right now

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.440
Ruochu

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:37.240
What do you think?

00:08:40.679 --> 00:08:41.919
You're asking me?

00:08:42.879 --> 00:08:43.840
Come, sit down

00:08:49.399 --> 00:08:52.720
You will be the one to launch our website

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:11.759
Okay

00:09:12.559 --> 00:09:14.200
Finally, a big task is done

00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:15.360
Now,

00:09:15.879 --> 00:09:16.919
we need to figure out how to promote it

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.440
and attract more users

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:24.639
Did you bring money?

00:09:25.200 --> 00:09:25.799
What for?

00:09:25.879 --> 00:09:26.600
I have an idea right now

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:27.639
I want to create a QQ group

00:09:27.639 --> 00:09:28.759
And pull everyone in

00:09:28.759 --> 00:09:30.080
I'll give them 50 cents for every person they invite

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:31.480
I'll give them 50 cents for every person they invite

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:32.879
Then, once we grow this QQ group big enough,

00:09:32.879 --> 00:09:34.399
they'll help us promote it vigorously

00:09:34.399 --> 00:09:35.279
No, no, Bro

00:09:35.519 --> 00:09:36.279
Although I don't understand,

00:09:36.519 --> 00:09:37.600
just take however much you need

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:40.440
Consider this money a loan to you

00:09:40.799 --> 00:09:41.519
When things take off later,

00:09:42.399 --> 00:09:42.960
I'll pay you back double

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:44.080
Bro

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:44.840
You're too kind

00:09:52.639 --> 00:09:54.559
The admin of each group will be in charge

00:09:54.799 --> 00:09:55.840
Create another group just for admins

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.360
You'll be responsible for these people

00:09:58.360 --> 00:09:58.799
Oh

00:09:59.519 --> 00:10:01.080
Five cents per post

00:10:01.759 --> 00:10:03.399
Everyone, comment more

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:04.759
Post more

00:10:05.639 --> 00:10:09.679
Say plenty of good things about our DomainNet

00:10:10.440 --> 00:10:12.320
We've got our first batch of users. That's it for now

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:14.000
There can't be a next time

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.840
The rest of the promotion depends on our own efforts

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:38.240
Hello, Mom

00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:39.159
My classmates are having a dinner party

00:10:39.159 --> 00:10:40.039
Everyone is going

00:10:40.679 --> 00:10:41.559
I'll be home a bit late

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:43.440
Don't wait up for me

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:49.080
I haven't been able to log in since this morning

00:10:51.039 --> 00:10:52.480
Looks like it's a professional hacker

00:10:53.240 --> 00:10:54.039
Who could be behind this?

00:10:54.879 --> 00:10:55.639
No matter who it is,

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.320
since they want to play dirty,

00:10:57.679 --> 00:10:59.039
then don't blame me for not holding back